Featuring covered waterside front porch, great room with gas fireplace, formal dining room, spacious eat-in kitchen, half bath, and laundry on first floor. Master suite with sitting room/office and full bath, and 2 additional bedrooms and full bath on second floor. Attached 2-car garage.
